snippet.title: Maxis - SimCity 2000: Special Edition for Windows 95 - 1995
snippet.description:
For those who wants to rememorate this city building / management game that was SimCity 2000: Special Edition for Windows 95 (also known as SimCity 2000: CD Collection) developed and published by Maxis Software Inc. in 1995.
